| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6078 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 647d8452-e797-5e03-b2b0-4bcc45b429e8"
